      p.blurb As part of Adobe Education Exchange's "UX to UI" online course, I redesigned an interior design website.
      h1.bc-mac bc-mac
      p In searching for a summer job, I stumbled upon the website for a local interior design and furniture store. It had an extensive number of usability issues. These included hard-to-read text and a lack of information architecture, on top of it not being responsive.

