      h1.big Reflection

  .flex
    .col-2
      p I missed an opportunity to talk to the store owner about these designs; by talking to him, I would've gained a better understanding of the users, as well as aligning my design with the store's brand. As this was more of a UI project, I didn't take the store's mission and values into consideration either; the focus of the project was more on reorganizing the website, and making aesthetic changes. Were I to take this on a second time, I would work directly with the store owner and a web developer to make sure I was staying on-brand.
